based on their living conditions.

00:23:20.484 --> 00:23:23.320
In this case, neither the plaintiff
nor the defendants

00:23:23.403 --> 00:23:25.822
are the real parties here.

00:23:26.406 --> 00:23:29.785
If anything,
they're all just victims of the affair.

00:23:34.456 --> 00:23:35.457
Let's do this.

00:23:35.541 --> 00:23:38.460
