who are minors.

00:23:49.388 --> 00:23:51.348
Just have Lee Sujin attend.

00:23:52.891 --> 00:23:54.852
Yes, Your Honor.
I'll talk to the plaintiff.

00:23:58.146 --> 00:24:02.067
